x=\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\sec(u)\Longrightarrow dx=\frac2{\sqrt3}\tan(u)\sec(u)\;du
\int{\frac{x-1}{x\sqrt{3x^2-4}}}\;dx
\int{\frac{x-1}{x\sqrt{3x^2-4}}}\;dx=\int{\frac{1}{\sqrt{3x^2-4}}}\;dx-\int{\frac{1}{x\sqrt{3x^2-4}}}\;dx\Longrightarrow
\int{\frac{1}{\sqrt{3x^2-4}}}\;dx-\int{\frac{1}{x\sqrt{3x^2-4}}}\;dx=
\frac{2}{\sqrt3}\int\frac{\tan(u)\sec(u)}{2\sqrt{\left(\frac{\sqrt3}{2}\sec(u)\right)^2-1}}\;du-\frac1{2}\int\frac{\frac{\sqrt3}{2}}{\frac{\sqrt3}{2}x\sqrt{\left(\frac{\sqrt3}{2}x\right)^2-1}}\;dx=
\frac{1}{\sqrt3}\int\sec{u}\;du-\frac12\sec^{-1}\left(\frac{\sqrt3}{2}x\right)
\frac{1}{\sqrt3}\log\left|\sqrt3x+\sqrt{3x^2-4}\right|-\frac12\sec^{-1}{\left(\frac{\sqrt3}{2}x\right)}+C
\int\sec(t)dt=\log|\sec t+\tan t|
\sec u=\frac{\sqrt{3}x}{2}
\tan u=\frac{\sqrt{3x^2-4}}{2}
\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\log\left|\frac{\sqrt{3}x+\sqrt{3x^2-4}}{2}\right|.
\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\log\left|\sqrt{3}x+\sqrt{3x^2-4}\right|-\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\log 2.
\tan t=\frac{\sqrt{3x^2-2}}{2}
\cos t=\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}x} 
x=\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\sec t \Rightarrow dx=\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\sec t \tan t dt
\int \frac{x-1}{x\sqrt{3x^2-4}}dx=\int \frac{(\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\sec t-1)}{\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\sec t\cdot 2\tan t} \cdot \frac{2}{\sqrt{3}}\sec t\tan t dt=\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\int\sec t dt- \frac{1}{2}\int dt=
=\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\ln |\sec t+\tan t|-\frac{1}{2}t +c= 
\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}}\ln |\frac{\sqrt{3}x}{2}+\frac{\sqrt{3x^2-4}}{2}|-\frac{1}{2}\arccos(\frac{2}{\sqrt{3}x})+c.  
